<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>المَفْعُولِ مَعَهُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهُوَ:</span> الِاسْمُ المَنْصُوبُ الَّذِي يُذْكَرُ لِبَيَانِ مَنْ فُعِلَ مَعَهُ الفِعْلُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">نَحْوُ قَوْلِكَ:</span> جَاءَ الأَمِيرُ وَالجَيْشَ، وَاسْتَوَى المَاءُ وَالخَشَبَةَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>* * *<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَأَمَّا خَبَرُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«كَانَ»</span> وَأَخَوَاتِهَا، وَاسْمُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«إِنَّ»</span> وَأَخَوَاتِهَا: فَقَدْ تَقَدَّمَ ذِكْرُهُمَا فِي <span style="color:#6c6c00">«المَرْفُوعَاتِ»</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَكَذَلِكَ التَّوَابِعُ:</span> فَقَدْ تَقَدَّمَتْ هُنَاكَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>* * *<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>